description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Mischievous Experimental 2D Gameplay. Sometimes, game prototypes go badly. Here you can play quite a few of those. Some twisted, some evil, and most of them plainly unfair. Enjoy!
